               Zhang, Yufeng and Zuo, Zhong and Chan, Renee Wan Yi and Ng,
               Billy Wai-Lung",
  abstract  = "Nucleoside analogues are effective antiviral agents, and the
               continuous emergence of pathogenic viruses demands the
               development of novel and structurally diverse analogues. Here,
               we present the design and synthesis of novel nucleoside
               analogues with a carbobicyclic core, which mimics the
